gargantuintutil

Class Gargantuint

  • java.lang.Object
    • gargantuintutil.Gargantuint

  • public class Gargantuint
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles arbitrarily large integers and has the ability to perform basic arithmetic calculations on these large integers such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, division and equality comparison.
